title: EMC ScaleIO: Volume size and throughput
agents: linux
catalog: os/storage/emc
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the total size and the user r/w of a volume. The ruleset
 "Levels for disk IO" can be used to set thresholds for read/write throughput.

item:
 The volume id is used as item

inventory:
 One service for each volume is created
